(73, 'The Unsung Hero of a Perfect Crown: Why We Insist on Using a flender wedge', NULL, '<p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Hello everyone,</span></p><p><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/dr.kiranrajumds/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Dr. D.V.S. Kiran Raju</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"> </span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">here, M.D.S., from Srinivasa Multispeciality Dental Hospital in Kakinada—recognized by many of our patients as one of the </span><a href=\"https://srinivasadentalkakinada.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">best dental hospitals in Kakinada</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">When you choose to get a dental crown, you\'re not just repairing a tooth—you’re restoring the strength, function, and natural beauty of your smile. As the</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"> </span><a href=\"https://srinivasadentalkakinada.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">best dentist in Kakinada</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, I believe perfection lies in the smallest details. One such detail, often overlooked but incredibly important, is the use of a</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"> flender wedge</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> during crown and filling procedures.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">You may have heard me discuss this in a recent video. It may seem like just a tiny plastic or wooden piece, but this flender wedge plays a vital role in ensuring long-lasting, comfortable results. Let me explain why we always use it, especially during dental crown treatments and </span><a href=\"https://srinivasadentalkakinada.com/rootcanal.php\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">root canal treatments in Kakinada.</a></p>', NULL, '<h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">What Is a Flender wedge?</strong></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">A flender wedge is a small, triangular tool that we gently insert between the tooth being treated and the adjacent tooth. Although it’s in place for only a short time, its effects are long-lasting—protecting neighboring teeth and helping us achieve a seamless, precise fit for your restoration.</span></p><h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">3 Reasons We Use a flender wedge During Treatment</strong></h3><h4><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(33, 154, 2);\">1. It Protects Adjacent Teeth</strong></h4><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">When shaping a tooth for a </span><a href=\"https://srinivasadentalkakinada.com/bridgetreatment.php\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">dental crown treatment</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">,</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> we use high-speed tools that need to be extremely precise. The wedge acts as a protective barrier, preventing any accidental damage to the healthy enamel of the tooth next to it. This small step helps avoid future dental problems and preserves your natural teeth.</span></p><h4><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(33, 154, 2);\">2. It Helps Achieve a Natural, Snug Fit</strong></h4><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Patients who come to us from other clinics often say,</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><em style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\"Food keeps getting stuck next to my new crown.\"</em></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">This issue arises when the contact point between two teeth is not properly restored. By using a flender wedge, we create the ideal amount of separation during the procedure, allowing us to design a crown or filling that fits perfectly—just like your natural teeth. This ensures:</span></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">No food getting trapped</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Healthy gums</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Easy, effective flossing</span></li></ol><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">This level of precision is one of the reasons patients trust us for</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"> </span><a href=\"https://srinivasadentalkakinada.com/rootcanal.php\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">root canal treatment in Kakinada</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"> </span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">and crown work.</span></p><h4><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(33, 154, 2);\">3. It Prevents Tooth Sensitivity</strong></h4><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">By preventing accidental contact with adjacent teeth, the flender wedge helps maintain the enamel’s integrity. This reduces the risk of post-procedure sensitivity, ensuring your new crown or filling feels comfortable from day one.</span></p><h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Why Patients Choose Us</strong></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">At </span><a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/iAmX5Q7\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Srinivasa Multispeciality Dental Hospital</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, we go beyond just fixing teeth—we focus on quality, longevity, and patient comfort. Whether you’re visiting us for a root canal treatment, a dental crown, or any other procedure, we incorporate these small tools and techniques to give you the best possible outcome.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Our attention to detail is what makes us stand out as one of the </span><a href=\"https://g.co/kgs/iAmX5Q7\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">best dental hospitals in Kakinada</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">—and why many patients consider Dr. D.V.S. Kiran Raju among the best dentists in Kakinada.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">We believe in empowering our patients by explaining the </span><em style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">why</em><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> behind every step of treatment. Using a flender wedge is just one example of how we prioritize excellence in every procedure.</span></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Have questions about your crown or root canal?</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Or looking for a clinic that combines precision with compassion?</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">We’d love to welcome you for a consultation at our clinic.</span></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Stay healthy and keep smiling,</strong></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Dr. D.V.S. Kiran Raju, M.D.S</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Srinivasa Multispeciality Dental Hospital</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </span><em style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Kakinada, Andhra Pradesh</em></p><p><br></p>', NULL, '<p><br></p>', NULL, '<p><br></p>', NULL, '<p><br></p>', NULL, '', '', '', '', '6936abf0a9404_1765190640.png', '6936abf0a95fe_1765190640.mp4', '', '', 'Root Canal', '2025-07-14 06:46:27');
