(74, 'Think Before You Bite: The Truth About 4 AM Biryani and Your Oral Health By Dr. D.V.S. Kiran Raju, M.D.S., Chief Dentist at Srinivasa Multispeciality Dental Hospital, Kakinada', '4 AM బిర్యానీ లవర్స్ జాగ్రత్త! మీ క్రేవింగ్స్ మీ పళ్లకు ముప్పు తెస్తున్నాయా?', '<p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">In recent times, we’ve noticed an unusual yet rapidly growing trend — the habit of eating </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">biryani at 4 AM or early in the morning</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, especially among youngsters. Whether it\'s due to night shifts, hostel life, or just midnight cravings, this trend has become a lifestyle for many. As a dental expert, I must warn that such eating habits can silently affect your oral health.</span></p><p><br></p>', '<p><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">- డాక్టర్ డి.వి.ఎస్. కిరణ్ రాజు, M.D.S. (శ్రీనివాస మల్టీస్పెషాలిటీ డెంటల్ హాస్పిటల్, కాకినాడ)</strong></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">ఈ రోజుల్లో రాత్రి షిఫ్టులు చేసేవారు లేదా హాస్టల్స్ లో ఉండేవారు తెల్లవారుజామున 4 గంటలకు బిర్యానీ తినడం ఒక ట్రెండ్‌గా మారింది. బిర్యానీతో పాటు థమ్స్ అప్ వంటి కూల్ డ్రింక్స్ తాగడం ఇంకా ఎక్కువైంది. కానీ, దంత వైద్యునిగా నేను చెప్పేది ఏమిటంటే.. ఈ అలవాటు మీ పళ్ల ఆరోగ్యాన్ని నిశ్శబ్దంగా దెబ్బతీస్తుంది.</span></p><p><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">What’s even more concerning is the common pairing of </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">spicy biryani with fizzy drinks like Thums Up</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">. Biryani is rich in spices, oil, and carbohydrates, while sodas are highly acidic and sugary. Together, they create the perfect storm for your teeth — </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">acids that erode enamel</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, sugars that feed harmful bacteria, and poor timing that denies your mouth the natural defense of saliva, especially during sleep hours.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">If you\'re indulging in this trend without brushing before or after, you are unknowingly increasing your risk of cavities, gum disease, bad breath, and enamel erosion.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">At Srinivasa Multispeciality Dental Hospital, recognized as one of the</span><a href=\"https://srinivasadentalkakinada.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </a><a href=\"https://srinivasadentalkakinada.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">best dental hospitals in Kakinada</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, we see these issues becoming more common among young adults who follow irregular eating schedules.</span></p><h2><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Why Eating Without Brushing Is a Problem</strong></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">During sleep, your saliva production slows down. Saliva is essential for cleansing the mouth by flushing out bacteria and leftover food particles. If you eat without brushing after a full night’s bacterial buildup, you’re essentially feeding those germs and allowing them to multiply rapidly.</span></p><h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Common Issues That Arise:</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(33, 154, 2);\">Tooth Decay</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: Sugars and starches in food fuel harmful bacteria that produce acids, which erode enamel.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(33, 154, 2);\">Bad Breath</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: Food particles stuck between teeth combine with overnight bacteria to cause strong odor.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(33, 154, 2);\">Gum Infections</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: Plaque buildup from such habits can irritate and infect your gums over time.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(33, 154, 2);\">Enamel Erosion</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: Acidic foods or beverages at odd hours worsen enamel damage, especially if you brush immediately after.</span></li></ol><h2><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">The 4 AM Biryani Effect: More Than Just a Craving</strong></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Biryani is a complex dish loaded with spices, oil, and refined carbohydrates — all of which can easily cling to your teeth and gumline. When consumed at 4 AM — a time when your mouth is least active in defense — it becomes a silent destroyer of oral health.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Add to that the fizzy soda pairing like Thums Up, and you\'re inviting more harm. These beverages are highly acidic and sugary, amplifying the damage to your tooth enamel and promoting bacterial growth.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Dr. D.V.S. Kiran Raju</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, widely regarded as one of the</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"> best dentists in Kakinada</span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, emphasizes that maintaining oral hygiene during unconventional eating hours is essential in preserving long-term dental health.</span></p><h2><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Tips to Break the Habit:</strong></h2><ol><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(33, 154, 2);\">Brush Before Late-Night Meals</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: If you\'re about to eat at an odd hour, brush first — even a quick rinse is better than nothing.</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(33, 154, 2);\">Rinse Thoroughly After Eating</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: Swish water or a mouthwash immediately after eating.</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(33, 154, 2);\">Limit Sugary or Acidic Late-Night Foods</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: Choose lighter, less sticky snacks if you must eat late.</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(33, 154, 2);\">Keep Oral Hygiene Essentials Handy</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: A travel toothbrush or mouthwash near your bed can help reduce laziness.</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(33, 154, 2);\">Get Regular Checkups</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">: Early detection is key to avoiding major dental problems.</span></li></ol><h2><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">When Should You Be Concerned?</strong></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">If you’re noticing constant bad breath, visible tooth damage, bleeding gums, or increased sensitivity, it’s a strong sign that you should seek a dental consultation.. At </span><a href=\"https://share.google/u2NqAX4Ybc4M43VAr\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Srinivasa Multispeciality Dental Hospital in Kakinada</a><a href=\"https://share.google/u2NqAX4Ybc4M43VAr\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">,</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> our expert team offers thorough dental checkups and personalized treatments. That’s why we are trusted as the </span><a href=\"https://share.google/u2NqAX4Ybc4M43VAr\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">best dental hospital in Kakinada</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> for preventive and restorative dental care.</span></p><h2><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Final Thoughts from Dr. Kiran Raju</strong></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\"Oral health isn’t just about brushing in the morning and at night. It’s about being mindful of </span><em style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">when</em><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> and </span><em style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">how</em><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> you eat — especially during odd hours like 4 AM. Your teeth work hard for you 24/7; the least you can do is not feed them biryani in the dark!\"</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> — </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Dr. D.V.S. Kiran Raju, M.D.S., Chief Dentist</strong></p><h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">For Appointments and Expert Dental Care:</strong></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">📍 </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Srinivasa Multispeciality Dental Hospital, Kakinada</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> 📞 </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Call: 92900 19948</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> 🌐 </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Visit:</strong><a href=\"https://srinivasadentalkakinada.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </a><u style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);\"><a href=\"https://srinivasadentalkakinada.com\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://srinivasadentalkakinada.com</a></u></p><p><br></p>', '<h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">బిర్యానీ + కూల్ డ్రింక్: పళ్లకు శత్రువులు!</strong></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">బిర్యానీలో ఉండే మసాలాలు, నూనెలు మరియు కార్బోహైడ్రేట్లు పళ్ల సందుల్లో త్వరగా ఇరుక్కుపోతాయి. దీనికి తోడు కూల్ డ్రింక్స్‌లో ఉండే యాసిడ్స్ మరియు షుగర్ పళ్లపై ఉండే రక్షణ పొరను (Enamel) కరిగించేస్తాయి.</span></p><h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">తెల్లవారుజామున తినడం వల్ల వచ్చే సమస్యలు:</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">లాలాజలం తగ్గడం:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> మనం పడుకునే సమయంలో నోట్లో లాలాజలం (Saliva) తక్కువగా ఉత్పత్తి అవుతుంది. లాలాజలం పళ్లను శుభ్రం చేయడానికి సహాయపడుతుంది. అది తక్కువగా ఉన్నప్పుడు బిర్యానీ తింటే, బ్యాక్టీరియా పళ్లపై త్వరగా దాడి చేస్తుంది.</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">పిప్పికళ్లు (Cavities):</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> పళ్ల సందుల్లో ఇరుక్కున్న ఆహారం వల్ల బ్యాక్టీరియా పెరిగి రంధ్రాలు పడతాయి.</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">నోటి దుర్వాసన:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> రాత్రంతా నోట్లో పేరుకుపోయిన బ్యాక్టీరియా, మనం తిన్న ఆహారంతో కలిసి తీవ్రమైన దుర్వాసనకు కారణమవుతుంది.</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">చిగుళ్ల వాపు:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> ప్లాక్ పేరుకుపోవడం వల్ల చిగుళ్లు ఎర్రబడటం లేదా రక్తం కారడం జరుగుతుంది.</span></li></ol><h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">మీ దంతాలను ఎలా కాపాడుకోవాలి? (Tips by Dr. Kiran Raju):</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">తినకముందు బ్రష్ చేయండి:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent;