(78, 'How Smoking and Vaping Damage Your Teeth and Gums – What You Must Know!', 'సిగరెట్ లేదా వేపింగ్ అలవాటు ఉందా? మీ చిరునవ్వుకు పొంచి ఉన్న ముప్పు ఇదే!', '<p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Your smile is one of your greatest assets—it reflects your confidence and personality. But habits like smoking and vaping can silently destroy that healthy, radiant smile. While these practices might seem fashionable or relaxing, the truth is that they come with serious consequences for your dental and overall health. From yellow teeth and bad breath to gum infections, tooth loss, and oral cancer, the damage goes far beyond what meets the eye.</span></p><p><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">మీ అందమైన చిరునవ్వు మీ ఆత్మవిశ్వాసానికి నిదర్శనం. కానీ స్మోకింగ్ (సిగరెట్లు) మరియు వేపింగ్ (E-cigarettes) వంటి అలవాట్లు మీ పళ్లను, చిగుళ్లను లోలోపల నాశనం చేస్తాయి. చాలామంది వేపింగ్ సురక్షితం అనుకుంటారు, కానీ అది కూడా స్మోకింగ్ అంత ప్రమాదకరమే!</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">కాకినాడలోని </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">శ్రీనివాస మల్టీస్పెషాలిటీ డెంటల్ హాస్పిటల్</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> లో </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">డాక్టర్ డి.వి.ఎస్. కిరణ్ రాజు (MDS)</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> గారి పర్యవేక్షణలో, ఇటువంటి అలవాట్ల వల్ల దెబ్బతిన్న దంతాలకు మెరుగైన చికిత్స అందిస్తున్నాము.</span></p><p><br></p>', '<p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">At </span><a href=\"https://srinivasadentalkakinada.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Srinivasa Multispeciality Dental Hospital, Kakinada</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, we care about your smile and well-being. Our expert team, led by </span><a href=\"https://srinivasadentalkakinada.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">Dr. D.V.S. Kiran Raju, MDS</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, emphasizes awareness and preventive care for every patient. Let’s explore how smoking and vaping impact your teeth and gums—and what you can do to protect yourself.</span></p><h2><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">How Smoking and Vaping Affect Oral Health</strong></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Both smoking and vaping introduce harmful chemicals into your mouth. Cigarettes contain nicotine and tar, while e-cigarettes often include toxic substances like formaldehyde and heavy metals. These chemicals not only stain teeth but also interfere with saliva production, alter the pH balance in your mouth, and damage gum tissues.</span></p><h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Key Oral Health Issues Caused by Smoking and Vaping:</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Tooth Staining &amp; Discoloration</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Nicotine and tar cause deep yellow or brown stains that cannot be removed by regular brushing.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Persistent Bad Breath (Halitosis)</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Dry mouth and bacteria buildup lead to chronic bad breath.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Gum Disease (Periodontitis)</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Smoking weakens the immune system and reduces blood flow to gums, increasing infection risk.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Tooth Loss</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Advanced gum disease loosens teeth, often resulting in tooth extraction.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Delayed Healing</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Smoking slows healing after tooth extractions, implants, or other surgeries.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Oral Cancer Risk</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Both smoking and vaping significantly raise the chances of cancers affecting the lips, tongue, and throat.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Dry Mouth</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Lack of saliva makes teeth prone to decay and cavities.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Weakened Enamel</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Acidic chemicals in vape liquids and smoke erode tooth enamel, leading to sensitivity.</span></li></ol><p><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Why Quitting Smoking and Vaping is Essential</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Giving up smoking and vaping is not only good for your lungs and heart—it’s a game-changer for your oral health. Every cigarette or vape session accelerates dental damage, so quitting immediately reduces future risks.</span></p><h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(33, 154, 2);\">Benefits of Quitting:</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Brighter Teeth</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Eliminate stubborn stains and enjoy a whiter smile.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Healthier Gums</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Lower risk of infections, bleeding gums, and gum recession.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Faster Healing</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Recover quickly from dental treatments and surgeries.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Reduced Cancer Risk</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Protect yourself from life-threatening oral and throat cancers.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Improved Confidence</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Say goodbye to bad breath and smile freely again.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Financial Savings</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Save money on cigarettes, vapes, and expensive dental treatments.</span></li></ol><h2><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">How Your Life Improves After Quitting</strong></h2><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">A confident, natural smile that looks and feels great.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Stronger gums and better oral hygiene.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Fewer dental complications during treatments like implants or extractions.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Lower chances of severe conditions like oral cancer.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Better general health and overall quality of life.</span></li></ol><h2><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Tips to Quit Smoking and Vaping Successfully</strong></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Quitting may seem challenging, but it’s the best decision for your smile and overall health. Here’s how to start your journey:</span></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Set a Clear Quit Date</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Pick a date and stick to it.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Avoid Triggers</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Stay away from situations that tempt you to smoke or vape.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Seek Support</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Share your goal with family and friends for encouragement.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Use Nicotine Replacement Therapies (NRTs)</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Patches, gums, or lozenges can help.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Consider Behavioral Therapy</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Professional counseling reduces relapse chances.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Stay Active</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Exercise helps fight cravings and stress.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Avoid Alcohol</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Alcohol can weaken your determination to quit.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Reduce Gradually</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Slowly cut down before stopping completely if necessary.</span></li></ol><h2><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">What Happens When You Visit Srinivasa Multispeciality Dental Hospital?</strong></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">When you choose us for your oral health care, you’re in safe hands. Here’s what to expect during your visit:</span></p><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Comprehensive Oral Examination</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – We identify early signs of smoking-related damage.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Personalized Treatment Plans</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Customized care based on your dental condition.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Advanced Dental Procedures</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – From professional cleaning to gum treatment and implants.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Expert Guidance on Quitting Smoking</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> – Support to help you break free from harmful habits.</span></li></ol><h2><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Why We’re the Best Choice for Your Oral Health</strong></h2><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">At Srinivasa Multispeciality Dental Hospital, Kakinada, our priority is to provide top-quality dental care with compassion and expertise. We are recognized as the</span><a href=\"https://share.google/VOkohHuAl98J9CnRF\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> </a><a href=\"https://share.google/VOkohHuAl98J9CnRF\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">best dental hospital in Kakinada</a><a href=\"https://share.google/VOkohHuAl98J9CnRF\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">,</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> offering a complete range of dental treatments. Under the guidance of Dr. D.V.S. Kiran Raju, MDS, one of the</span><a href=\"https://share.google/VOkohHuAl98J9CnRF\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"> best dentists in Kakinada</a><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">, ensures pain-free, effective, and lasting solutions for every patient.</span></p><h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">Ready to Take Control of Your Smile?</strong></h3><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Don’t let smoking or vaping damage your teeth, gums, and confidence. Visit </span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Srinivasa Multispeciality Dental Hospital</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> today and let our expert team help you achieve a healthier smile.</span></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Address:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Srinivasa Multispeciality Dental Hospital, Jawahar Street, Beside MRF Showroom, Opp. Vivekananda Statue, Kulaicheruvu Park, Kakinada-1</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Phone:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> +91-08842342346 | +91-9290019948</span></p><p><br></p><h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">FAQs</strong></h3><p><br></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">1. Does smoking always cause yellow teeth?</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Yes. Nicotine and tar stain your teeth significantly, often requiring professional whitening or cleaning.</span></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">2. Is vaping safer for your oral health than smoking?</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Not really. Vaping can cause dry mouth, enamel erosion, and gum irritation, making it just as harmful.</span></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">3. Can gum disease caused by smoking be treated?</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Yes, if detected early. Scaling, deep cleaning, and proper care can help restore gum health.</span></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">4. How soon does oral health improve after quitting?</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Within weeks, you’ll notice fresher breath and healthier gums. Over time, your oral cancer risk decreases.</span></p><p><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">5. Can dentists help patients quit smoking?</strong></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> Absolutely. At Srinivasa Multispeciality Dental Hospital, we provide guidance, therapies, and support to help you quit.</span></p><p><br></p>', '<h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">స్మోకింగ్ &amp; వేపింగ్ వల్ల కలిగే దంత సమస్యలు:</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">పళ్లు పచ్చబడటం:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> సిగరెట్లోని నికోటిన్ మరియు తారు వల్ల పళ్లు పసుపు లేదా బ్రౌన్ కలర్‌లోకి మారిపోతాయి. ఇవి బ్రష్ చేసినా పోవు.</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">నోటి దుర్వాసన:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> నోరు ఎండిపోవడం (Dry Mouth) వల్ల బ్యాక్టీరియా పెరిగి, విపరీతమైన నోటి దుర్వాసన వస్తుంది.</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">చిగుళ్ల వ్యాధులు:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> స్మోకింగ్ వల్ల చిగుళ్లకు రక్తప్రసరణ తగ్గి ఇన్ఫెక్షన్లు త్వరగా వస్తాయి. దీనివల్ల పళ్లు వదులై ఊడిపోయే అవకాశం ఉంది.</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">గాయాలు త్వరగా మానవు:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> ఏదైనా పన్ను తీయించుకున్నా లేదా ఇంప్లాంట్ వేయించుకున్నా, స్మోకింగ్ చేసేవారికి ఆ గాయం మానడానికి చాలా సమయం పడుతుంది.</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">నోటి క్యాన్సర్:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> ధూమపానం వల్ల నాలుక, పెదవులు మరియు గొంతు క్యాన్సర్ వచ్చే ప్రమాదం చాలా ఎక్కువ.</span></li><li data-list=\"ordered\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">ఎనామెల్ దెబ్బతినడం:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> వేపింగ్‌లో ఉండే కెమికల్స్ వల్ల పళ్లపై ఉండే రక్షణ పొర (Enamel) అరిగిపోయి పళ్లు సెన్సిటివిటీకి గురవుతాయి.</span></li></ol><h3><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">ఈ అలవాట్లను మానేస్తే కలిగే లాభాలు:</strong></h3><ol><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">తెల్లని పళ్లు:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> మీ పళ్లపై మరకలు తగ్గి, నవ్వు ప్రకాశవంతంగా మారుతుంది.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">ఆరోగ్యకరమైన చిగుళ్లు:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> ఇన్ఫెక్షన్లు మరియు రక్తం కారే సమస్యలు తగ్గుతాయి.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">క్యాన్సర్ ముప్పు తప్పుతుంది:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> భయంకరమైన నోటి క్యాన్సర్ నుండి మిమ్మల్ని మీరు కాపాడుకోవచ్చు.</span></li><li data-list=\"bullet\"><span class=\"ql-ui\" contenteditable=\"false\"></span><strong style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">ఆర్థిక పొదుపు:</strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> సిగరెట్ల ఖర్చుతో పాటు, భవిష్యత్తులో అయ్యే భారీ డెంటల్ ఖర్చులను కూడా ఆదా చేయవచ్చు.</span><